Package: timeR
Type: Package
Title: Time Your Codes
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Yifu Yan
Maintainer: Yifu Yan <yanyifu94@hotmail.com>
Description: timeR package creates a R6 class, which allows you to create a 
    timer object to easily time your codes. Meanwhile, all records are saved to a 
    data frame, so it's easy to retrieve all the records for later use.
URL: https://github.com/yusuzech/timeR
BugReports: https://github.com/yusuzech/timeR/issues
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
Imports: R6
